          <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Continuing the discussion from <a href="https://socialhub.activitypub.rocks/t/which-links-between-activitypub-and-solid-project/529/10">Which links between ActivityPub and Solid project?</a>:</p>
<p>Hey <a class="mention" href="/u/rishabh">@rishabh</a>, <a class="mention" href="/u/falco">@Falco</a>: we have more and more the case that discussions spread across Discourse instances, it would be <em>very nice™</em> to have something that helps us federate those topics over ActivityPub. I’ve seen that ActivityPub support is not on the menu for the upcoming version 2.5 that just started. Do you have any plans moving forward? Do you need help?</p>
